                "abstract": "© 2019 The Author(s) . Published by Oxford University Press. All rights reserved.CoBAMP is a modular framework for the enumeration of pathway analysis concepts, such as elementary flux modes (EFM) and minimal cut sets in genome-scale constraint-based models (CBMs) of metabolism. It currently includes the K-shortest EFM algorithm and facilitates integration with other frameworks involving reading, manipulation and analysis of CBMs.",
